Reads images from openni driver, serializes and transfers them over tcp.

debian dependencies:

needs libcv >= 2.2  (eventually build from source)

needs boost >= 1.48

apt-get install	libxmu-dev \
		libxi-dev \
		libusb-1.0-0 \
		libusb-dev \
		libhighgui-dev \
		libboost-dev \
		libboost-serialization-dev \
		libboost-system \
		libboost-streamio \
		libboost-test-dev \
		
